  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You form the essence of death itself into a ball of burning voidfire, which you throw at a target. Make a spell attack roll. On a success, the flame deals 3d6 fire damage, and, if the target is living, the flame deals an additional 1d4 void damage. On a critical success, the target takes double damage and takes @Damage[(1d4+((@item.rank -1)*2))[persistent,fire]] damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success </strong>The target takes double damage and 1d4 persistent fire damage.</p><p><strong>Success </strong>The target takes full damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1) </strong>The fire damage increases by 1d6. The void damage increases by 1d4. The persistent fire damage on a critical hit increases by 2.</p>"
